Game 2 OMUF<sub>BZ</sub>

1: par \leftarrow BZ.PG(1^{\kappa})

2: (pk, sk) \stackrel{\$}{\leftarrow} BZ.KG(par) \Rightarrow \text{honest signer model}

3: sid \leftarrow 0 \Rightarrow \text{no session yet}

4: (m_1, \sigma_1), \dots, (m_{\ell(\mathcal{A})}, \sigma_{\ell(\mathcal{A})}) \stackrel{\$}{\leftarrow} \mathcal{A}^{S_1, S_2, GH}(pk)

5: if \exists i \neq j : m_i = m_j \text{ or } \exists k \in \{1 \dots \ell(\mathcal{A})\} : BZ.Ver(pk, \sigma_k, m_k) = 0 : \text{return } 0

6: Q_{S_1}(\mathcal{A}) \leftarrow \#\{1 \leq k \leq sid \mid sess_k = \text{open}\} \Rightarrow \text{abandoned sessions}

7: Q_{S_2}(\mathcal{A}) \leftarrow \#\{1 \leq k \leq sid \mid sess_k = \text{closed}\}

8: \text{return } (\ell(\mathcal{A}) \geq Q_{S_2}(\mathcal{A}) + 1) ? 1 : 0
